donations.donation_comment: Keep up the fight! Each day will get more challenging but JT and his Globalist counterparts are outnumbered! Even though I don't live in Canada, I thank you all for leading the way and showing the world how it's done! 💪🗽
I support freedom! Having said that, I think the message should to public in general should be clearer about that then anti vaccine. Done a great job! May God give you wisdom in all your efforts.
I am in solidarity with you.
donations.donation_name: Support for peaceful protest for basic human rights

donations.donation_comment: Thanks to all those truckers.  Some that have helped me haul my grain into Canada to help feed beef.   Wonderful tasting beef that feeds our fellow neighbors.
God bless every one of the supporters! Keep fighting for our freedoms.

I see a whole army of Canadian's here in defiance of tyranny. You have come as free men, and free men you are. What would you do with that freedom? Will you keep standing? And many years from now, you'll be able to tell your children that you stood and told the enemies of liberty, "You may take our lives, but You will never take our freedom." (Braveheart paraphrased)  "Hold!  Hold!"
